{"tid":2401454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"佢係咪中意我？","createTime":"2021-02-09T17:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T12:18:31.000Z","uid":302373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bd44632c90181663ab317cd10e880e6ed08075","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"佢知我結咗婚，同時知我準備同老公離婚。<br />\n一個男人會唔會中意一個咁嘅女人？<br />\n唔知佢有冇女朋友、結左婚未，又唔方便問，但成日見佢 fb 一個人食好西。<br />\n<br />\n有次老公係街上面向我發癲，仲掉低左我係街，我覺得勁慘，忍唔住喊左出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁岩個朋友 whatsapp 我，我忍唔住周佢講我唔知點算好，老公咁對我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朋友雖然返緊工，但都照打電話俾我，安慰左我好耐... 仲讚我又靚又叻，唔怕第時搵唔到第二個。假設離婚後生活有問題，總會有人幫我咁話... <br />\n<br />\n佢間唔時就會關心我近況，又讚我靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係咪中意我呀？"},{"pid":"177a6ad560a5cda011d124736741edccad01b4b5","tid":2401454,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"離婚搵佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0023857b92d98abdccf9a7d56c6747e11b7adcc8","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"177a6ad560a5cda011d124736741edccad01b4b5","tid":2401454,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T17:54:28.000Z","msg":"離婚搵佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T17:56:53.000Z","msg":"佢話佢大我好多年，可以叫得佢做叔叔，有咩事、訓唔著可以搵佢。我唔識分係咪只係純粹安慰一個人既說話..."},{"pid":"6ea8e953c3438bc02699380c17381748bf17aa62","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"其實我冇諗咁多...只係有人係你低潮時關心你，感覺...都開心 dd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abeab5965ba5374e4abe998b679fce013368190","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"但如果一個男人，咁既情況，真係中意我既話，一早有表態啦下話？定係佢已經暗示左，只係我太遲鈍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係我哩刻身份，佢根本唔方便表態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d9f59745690582c1f8b5745e816ebeb61f3d10","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f6b7d4e580c6b7df8c25d3f0cba403325d6bc7","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29071d7456514c1a2b65430abcb87d9af7d91bd1","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf8700ca55670d707312df2c958b812a0130fb8","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c8973aef3ee635eb07d36a60d3e8bcbfc87a6b","tid":2401454,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"你之前啲post話俾老公打 真定假？<br />\n認真！人少少"},{"pid":"39b34931dfa2b81c5c6dd06753fe7e3493202a7b","tid":2401454,"uid":101522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T19:24:41.000Z","msg":"其實你個人怕寂寞又敏感咁容易就中意一個人<br />\n就算離左婚你都好容易又出事遇著d仆街"},{"pid":"8780d541a403ba0d0767c1dccd7fc4a69d96e877","tid":2401454,"uid":302373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57c8973aef3ee635eb07d36a60d3e8bcbfc87a6b","tid":2401454,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"你之前啲post話俾老公打 真定假？<br />\n認真！人少少"